Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.46,0:01:35.21,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A mysterious new era now begins...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.21,0:01:37.10,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}...a Monday 7 o'clock deduction show!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.10,0:01:38.73,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today, our criminal is Kaitō Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.73,0:01:40.20,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Even though he can fool everyone's eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:41.92,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'll protect the jewel and my dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.92,0:01:43.60,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:45.41,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.41,0:01:47.97,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.14,0:00:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:07.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko Suzuki here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.61,0:00:12.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, do you all remember this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:14.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, Jirokichi Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:19.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An executive advisor to the Suzuki Financial Group, and my uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.04,0:00:24.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, Kaitō Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}'s destined rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.17,0:00:29.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though Uncle's the only one who actually thinks that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:38.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Their cut-throat battle over the legendary mules, the Purple Nails, should be fresh in your minds, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.22,0:00:45.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember {\i1}why{\i0} Uncle made Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} his rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:50.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:53.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's just terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.07,0:00:55.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So tonight, just for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.53,0:01:00.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,enjoy a special project and recall the memorable first battle between Uncle and Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:07.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Staking the miracle of the seas, the Blue Wonder, Uncle sends Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} a challenge notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,0:01:14.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And in response, Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}'s white guise walks through the moonlit night sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:16.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's quite the illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:21.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As expected from the moonlight magician, Kaitō Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:32.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, everyone. Please take your time and enjoy Uncle and Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}'s first battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:33.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This concludes today's programming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:36.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your patronage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:40.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.23,0:03:43.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the one who wanted us to see this caper movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:51.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but the first part was so good that I expected more from this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:56.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they just did exactly the same thing! What was the point of doing a 'Part II'?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:58.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.21,0:04:00.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it was okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:02.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Okay' isn't enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:06.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Well, that's pretty much what a sequel is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why can't it happen somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.51,0:04:13.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A brilliant and huge case with a magnificent daredevil
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:17.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who'll make my heart pound so hard that I can't hear anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:20.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, weren't you the one who didn't want to see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:29.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, you think so too, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.24,0:04:35.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.95,0:04:40.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:42.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you run into somebody, you could at least apologise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:44.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.21,0:04:45.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, your bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:48.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A purse snatcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:52.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:56.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would I listen to a four-eyed brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:04:58.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sic 'im, Lupin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:29.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}'Lupin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:40.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,P-Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:48.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sure are rude to go touching a girl's purse!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:51.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll get a line or two in my documentary, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.23,0:05:56.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Young lady, hurry and call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:05:58.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.11,0:06:00.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.07,0:06:03.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you too, doggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:05.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.11,0:06:07.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if he got away from my faithful Lupin,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:14.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he'd never get away from my ultra-classic with a twin-cam 1500cc engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:18.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if it came to it, I've put in a few extra modifications to speed it up even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:25.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:26.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Uncle Jirokichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:31.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're Shirō's daughter, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.52,0:06:34.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't seen you since your {\i1}Shichigosan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:36.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Does she know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:37.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:42.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is my uncle, Jirokichi Suzuki. He's my father's cousin,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:44.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the executive advisor to the Suzuki Financial Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.19,0:06:45.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.99,0:06:52.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when'd you get back here? I heard you were on a trip for the last six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.49,0:06:54.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:59.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was circling the globe to find it, and now I finally did, I came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:01.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The perfect bait, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:03.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bait?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:04.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bait?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.13,0:07:10.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So many medals and trophies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:12.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Europe Open Golf Championship...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.51,0:07:14.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The USA Cup for Yachting...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.98,0:07:17.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The World Hamburger Eating Contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:20.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've won them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.49,0:07:22.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was this thing always here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.68,0:07:25.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's the figurehead from the Sea Goddess,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:33.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a ship said to have been unsinkable during the Age of Discovery, when pirates roamed the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:35.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Golden Goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.19,0:07:40.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The jewel she's holding in her right hand is said to have been formed from a mermaid's tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.03,0:07:44.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a legendary aquamarine that's said to have the power to prevent shipwrecks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:48.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's called the miracle of the seas, the Blue Wonder!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:53.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the bait you were talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:54.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:57.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the bait that'll lure {\i1}him{\i0} out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:01.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Him'?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:05.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the 72 years I've walked this Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:09.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,nothing has ever escaped me, Jirokichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:12.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got every prize I ever wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.64,0:08:15.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fulfilled every dream I ever had...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:19.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But one prey slipped through my fingers time and time again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:26.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He can get past the tightest security, and open the toughest safe like magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.05,0:08:30.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then that sinner calmly spreads his white wings and vanishes into the night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.55,0:08:33.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.97,0:08:35.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't possibly mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.30,0:08:38.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. His name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:40.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaitō Kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:42.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'To Kaitō Kid.'
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:51.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'I placed the Big Jewel you desire, the Blue Wonder, on the rooftop of my Great Museum in Shiodome.'
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:54.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'If you want it, come and get it.'
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:57.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Jirokichi Suzuki, executive advisor to the Suzuki Financial Group'.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:03.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wasted two pages of the morning paper on this challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:06.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This guy's got {\i1}way{\i0} too much money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:08.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But isn't it exciting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:11.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moron. Of course he's not gonna show.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:17.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This rich weirdo must be full of himself to issue this challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:20.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of idiot would walk into such an obvious trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:22.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He has a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:30.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Sonoko told me that Kid sent an e-mail to her uncle Jirokichi saying he was okay with the challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:32.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.11,0:09:33.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:36.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he'd drop by this Saturday to inspect the place beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:42.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, I had her forward the e-mail to my mobile.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:44.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:48.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'It is my pleasure to accept your challenge.'
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:51.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Let us meet on April 12th at 8 PM.'
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.50,0:09:54.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'I apologise in advance for dropping by on the night before to have a look around...'
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.92,0:09:57.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Kaitō Kid'.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:10:00.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's as snobbish as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:03.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, there's a 'P.S.' after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:04.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A postscript?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:10.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As befitting the name 'Blue Wonder', I will walk right up to it and take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:12.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Walk right up'?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:27.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.22,0:10:28.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't care who they are, make sure you check them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:32.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want a checkpoint on every road that leads to this museum!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.14,0:10:34.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't let a single suspicious person through!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:35.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.02,0:10:41.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, the helicopters are really noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.81,0:10:47.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? You don't know how to recognise Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:51.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just pinch their faces and pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:53.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.45,0:10:57.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when I say 'pull', I mean a good hard yank!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:10:58.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Really{\i0} hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.66,0:11:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:05.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Nakamori's really fired up...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.38,0:11:06.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:09.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.26,0:11:12.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:15.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's some entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:19.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey. Has Kaitō Kid showed up yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.93,0:11:22.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.11,0:11:30.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man with the tiny moustache is Ran's dad, Sleeping Kogorō{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.53,0:11:31.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Tiny moustache?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.15,0:11:34.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've heard a lot about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:37.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not that great...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:43.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, is it you? Are you the one responsible for this havoc?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:45.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do something about your helicopters!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.92,0:11:50.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're getting in the way of the {\i1}police{\i0} helicopters!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:53.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no need for police helicopters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.59,0:11:56.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't Kid say in his notice that he'd come on foot?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:12:00.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then what are {\i1}your{\i0} choppers doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:05.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're filming the epic documentary about my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.31,0:12:07.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Documentary?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.15,0:12:12.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.65,0:12:15.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's like a TV news van!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:18.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not just the helicopter cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:24.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can view the footage from cameras in over 100 places around the museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.41,0:12:28.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, there's nobody in the museum!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:38.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were too many before! Now even if he {\i1}does{\i0} sneak into the museum in disguise, he'll be completely obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:43.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the doors in the museum can be opened and closed from this van.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:50.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if he does get to the Goddess on the top floor, he'll just be trapped...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.07,0:12:55.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, that's if he has the guts to show up like he announced!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:00.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.66,0:13:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:08.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you zoom in a bit more?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:17.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So he's finally shown up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:20.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaitō Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:26.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, from which one is it?\NWhich helicopter's filming this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:28.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which helicopter is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:29.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's #7!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:31.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it's flying behind the museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.76,0:13:35.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Behind the museum?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:35.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:37.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}From behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:39.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:41.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:44.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just to be safe, should I activate the device that moves the Golden Goddess inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:46.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep your calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.95,0:13:50.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tonight, he's just casing the museum. He won't steal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.28,0:13:53.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he said he'd walk right up to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:54.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:56.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.57,0:13:57.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:14:04.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see how the great thief known as the 'Moonlight Magician' makes his appearance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:10.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:13.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is he? Where's Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:16.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He flew between the buildings and didn't come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:20.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come on... Step out of the shadows, Kaitō Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:23.97,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Your feet must touch the ground for you to walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.97,0:14:27.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come on... Come out, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:44.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:52.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way... It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:57.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}... Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}'s floating!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.17,0:14:58.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:05.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be... It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:08.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No human being can defy the law of gravity...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:12.06,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}...and float in the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:27.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't let him fool you! It's just one of his tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:33.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet he's just hanging from a wire suspended from a black balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.72,0:15:38.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go over him! Have one of the choppers nearby fly over his head!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.15,0:15:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-This is chopper #7.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:44.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing above Kid's head!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:45.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:48.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}'s so amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:50.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think so, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.53,0:15:55.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is chopper #7.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:57.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.25,0:15:58.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.91,0:15:59.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:03.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Kid! What trick did you use?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.46,0:16:04.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He can't just be floating!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.75,0:16:06.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Find that rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:12.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}My, such a mess. And this has just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:14.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's not above him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:16.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's beside him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:20.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Of course. He strung a wire between the buildings and is hanging from that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:22.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'll check the building on the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:24.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You go to the roof of the one on the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:25.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Find that wire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:26.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.98,0:16:28.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.49,0:16:30.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:32.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You won't make fools out of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.33,0:16:38.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the end, it's just a magic trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:41.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just you wait, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:43.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once you know how it's done...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:45.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:47.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no wire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.59,0:16:50.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-Nothing! There's no wire anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:55.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Nakamori! We can't find anything in this building either!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:57.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.22,0:16:59.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then how's he doing it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:01.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}How's he freely...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.81,0:17:08.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:19.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, for tonight... Pay attention to the miracle that I am performing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:29.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-He's walking...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:33.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow! He's walking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.31,0:17:41.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is chopper #3!\NKid's currently walking in mid-air!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:43.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's impossible! What trick is he using?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:56.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:59.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}'s walking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:03.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is chopper #3. Kid's currently walking over Shiodome Park!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.26,0:18:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At this rate, he'll reach the rooftop of the Great Suzuki Museum and grab the Blue Wonder
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.22,0:18:10.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in less than a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:25.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't we do anything other than watch him steal it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:27.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:30.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}How's he planning to escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:33.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There are cops on the ground, and choppers in the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.01,0:18:37.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Advisor! Surely it's time to activate the device!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:40.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:56.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is it for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:19:00.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll come back tomorrow at 8 PM, at the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:05.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:10.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did I tell you? You can't take Kid lightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:13.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have no intention of letting him steal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:17.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, I went all around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.18,0:19:20.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to get my hands on the miracle of the seas, the Blue Wonder!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:24.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why's the golden figurehead indoors, and upside-down?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:27.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is how the mechanism works.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:40.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, it rotates and replaces the real figurehead with a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:44.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid's bound to see through a cheap trick like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:47.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course. I don't expect him to fall for the forgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:54.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then tomorrow, instead of using your helicopters, you should just let the police take care of things!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:56.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the contrary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:19:58.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Contrary?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:20:02.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he'd appear at the same place tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.60,0:20:04.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I'll be there, waiting to ambush him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:08.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What ambush?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.73,0:20:12.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll rent every building and fill the block
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:16.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,with an army of helicopters and guards that'll dwarf the ones from today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.74,0:20:19.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what kind of hocus-pocus he used to walk in mid-air,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:22.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but if he shows up again regardless,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.16,0:20:25.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll catch him and put him in the final chapter of my epic documentary!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.81,0:20:29.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't move. Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.28,0:20:31.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.49,0:20:34.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.93,0:20:36.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Where is it? Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:38.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:45.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:47.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with this dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.46,0:20:53.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good old Lupin! Like me, you never let go of your prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.72,0:20:55.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A contact lens?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.43,0:20:58.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you had bad eyes, Uncle Jirokichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.06,0:21:04.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that I'm 72, this old body doesn't work the way it used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.06,0:21:06.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You don't say...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:09.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I want to capture him while I still can.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:12.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why are you so obsessed with Kaitō Kid, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.99,0:21:15.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid... Kaitō Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:19.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every time I hear that name, I remember that he took everything from me, that damn Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.29,0:21:21.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll never forgive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:27.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen! I, Jirokichi Suzuki, will capture him, and I won't let anyone get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.42,0:21:28.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody will stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.55,0:21:33.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've seen all the glories and prizes I've attained, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.43,0:21:37.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Each and every time, I've made the front page of the paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.14,0:21:39.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...except once!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.18,0:21:40.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You can't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.81,0:21:45.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! Not only did that petty thief get the front page, he got the second page too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.23,0:21:51.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My triumphant world trip in a self-powered aircraft got pushed back to just a corner of page three!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.24,0:21:53.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you comprehend the humiliation?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.24,0:21:56.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you understand the pain I've suffered?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.49,0:21:57.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it, I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.95,0:22:00.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when I capture him...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.45,0:22:04.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I, Jirokichi Suzuki, shall make my grand comeback to the front page!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.58,0:22:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been expecting you, Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.50,0:22:19.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.58,0:22:22.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've prepared seats for your guests as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.30,0:22:24.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey, hey, are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.09,0:22:26.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Isn't this the roof?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.59,0:22:31.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you care for a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.55,0:22:32.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.60,0:22:36.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is the first time I can actually see she's a wealthy heiress.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.14,0:22:40.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can really tell this is one of the buildings near the spot where Kid appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.81,0:22:43.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at all the guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.15,0:22:45.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I still don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.53,0:22:48.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I got a look at the footage filmed from that helicopter,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.99,0:22:51.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but there wasn't anything odd at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.57,0:22:54.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And then he disappeared in mid-air!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.62,0:22:56.16,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}How'd he do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.91,0:22:59.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.96,0:23:00.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:06.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Scratch marks! As if something was hooked here...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.55,0:23:09.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And they're still fresh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.47,0:23:11.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.72,0:23:14.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A veil of helicopters covers the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.31,0:23:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Countless security guards patrol the streets!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.06,0:23:22.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These elite forces were chosen by the Suzuki Financial Group for their supreme vigilance!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.98,0:23:26.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will {\i1}he{\i0} dare to appear in such a heavily guarded area?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.99,0:23:31.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm referring to the one who announced he would steal the Blue Wonder from the Suzuki Museum's roof...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.99,0:23:34.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...Kaitō Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.12,0:23:37.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll come, he'll come. Of course he'll come!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.00,0:23:42.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An heiress of the Suzuki Financial Group whose jewels are\Nbeing targeted {\i1}really{\i} shouldn't be saying something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.75,0:23:44.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's Kaitō Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.92,0:23:47.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to meet him in person at least once!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.88,0:23:55.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, I volunteered to sit on the museum's roof and hold the Goddess,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.89,0:23:58.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but Uncle Jirokichi wouldn't let me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.64,0:24:01.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course not...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.14,0:24:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You weren't hoping to get stolen along with the jewel, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.48,0:24:11.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You bet! Then Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} would show up to rescue me from captivity!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.66,0:24:16.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just thinking about having two men fighting for me like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.37,0:24:23.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I can understand the over-the-top security.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.12,0:24:29.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, we're talking about somebody who announced he was coming to inspect the scene
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.01,0:24:36.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then showed up floating in mid-air, walked to the museum, and vanished!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.55,0:24:41.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly, he looked like he was naturally\Nwalking in mid-air, as if there was no trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.39,0:24:44.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there had to be, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.15,0:24:49.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If people could walk in the sky that easily, it'd scare the birdies away!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.82,0:24:51.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-Birdies?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.65,0:24:54.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you're such a cute kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.70,0:24:57.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I think I overdid the kiddie talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.53,0:25:03.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid's magic should've amazed a child like you as much as the birdies.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.12,0:25:08.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know how he did the trick yet, but I think I found a clue!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.84,0:25:12.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, there's scratch marks on the wall there!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.51,0:25:15.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.47,0:25:17.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You found marks there too?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.93,0:25:19.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.64,0:25:21.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are scratches on the wall of the building you're in?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.94,0:25:24.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, and they're brand new!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.44,0:25:27.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what {\i1}are{\i0} they?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.07,0:25:30.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he ran a wire between the buildings.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.95,0:25:36.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaitō Kid could've hung from it to make it look like he was floating!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.20,0:25:41.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope. Inspector Nakamori was on the other building last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.67,0:25:45.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and he said there were no wires!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.19,0:25:52.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then do you know how he did it, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.50,0:25:53.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.97,0:25:55.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How was it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.81,0:25:59.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When people assume something is impossible,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.65,0:26:04.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,their preconceptions keep them from seeing it, even if it's right in front of their eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.86,0:26:06.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Preconceptions?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.65,0:26:07.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.36,0:26:09.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What didn't we notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.57,0:26:11.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.28,0:26:14.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe a huge sheet of solid glass!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.03,0:26:18.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid placed it between the two buildings and walked on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.79,0:26:24.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Nakamori didn't see it because he'd never imagined such an audacious trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.80,0:26:30.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The scratch marks must've been left by whatever he used to lock the glass down...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.18,0:26:34.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think nobody would notice a giant sheet of glass?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.01,0:26:35.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.51,0:26:40.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And how could he sneak it in and install it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.10,0:26:43.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I said 'maybe'...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.02,0:26:46.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Their preconceptions keep them from seeing it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.03,0:26:49.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.03,0:26:50.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-Inspector Nakamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.91,0:26:54.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's just too many people! We can't check everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.24,0:26:59.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Suzuki Financial Group seems to be handing out 'Welcome Kid Fans' flyers!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.00,0:27:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Flyers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.58,0:27:02.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we don't let them in, they'll riot!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.08,0:27:04.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No choice then.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.46,0:27:06.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let them in without checks if you have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.30,0:27:07.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.34,0:27:09.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's flying in anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.84,0:27:12.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must be the owner of the miracle of the seas, the Blue Wonder,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.39,0:27:15.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,as well as the executive advisor to the Suzuki Financial Group, Jirokichi Suzuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.57,0:27:16.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.11,0:27:19.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With one hour to go before the big moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.78,0:27:21.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,are you ready for Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.37,0:27:25.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll show off his cheap parlour tricks,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.62,0:27:28.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I'm the one who's going to be the protagonist in tonight's show.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.62,0:27:32.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll show you a scene of justice that'll beat any Hollywood movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.58,0:27:35.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle's in really high spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.75,0:27:37.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We now return to commercials...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.76,0:27:43.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The new place to be in Shiodome. The Great Suzuki Museum, filled with the scent of history and culture!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.76,0:27:47.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, even the {\i1}ads{\i} are about the museum!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.31,0:27:51.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's called synergy! Uncle's pretty good at this kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.40,0:27:55.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That aerial shot's just a clip from his TV special!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.86,0:27:58.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He might not look like it,\Nbut he's a calculating guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.74,0:28:04.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, Kaitō Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}! Come and steal my passionate heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.28,0:28:07.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's way too loud here for an intimate moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.04,0:28:09.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the wind's too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.95,0:28:10.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.28,0:28:12.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.04,0:28:15.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going down to see Mr. Jirokichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.29,0:28:18.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just noticed something neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.01,0:28:20.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.05,0:28:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.01,0:28:22.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.97,0:28:27.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want to look at the footage of Kaitō Kid from yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.10,0:28:27.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.97,0:28:30.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle Kogorō told me to watch it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.35,0:28:34.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you saw it over and over again last night, little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.48,0:28:39.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we already sent it down to the production staff working on the documentary.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.45,0:28:47.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll have to hand over all your footage to the police in the end, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.49,0:28:53.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, this is the first time that Kaitō Kid's been caught on film casing a target site.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.50,0:28:55.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.71,0:28:59.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why did Kid put on that demonstration?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.00,0:29:06.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Less than a minute to showtime! The Kid fans gathered here have started a countdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.14,0:29:09.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay tuned for the wondrous moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.22,0:29:12.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll never show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.27,0:29:19.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No magician would let the audience come on\Nstage and gather around him before the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.27,0:29:22.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'd see through his tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.28,0:29:29.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He announced he'd be appearing between those buildings tonight, so everyone's watching that spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.16,0:29:36.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the wind stirred up by my helicopters is too strong for his hang-glider.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.04,0:29:40.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way he can show his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.17,0:29:44.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not unless he's a {\i1}tengu{\i0} or a wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.19,0:30:01.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,K-Kaitō Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.32,0:30:10.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Kid! Kaitō Kid appeared just as he announced!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.99,0:30:12.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.62,0:30:14.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-He came...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.04,0:30:15.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he's really floating!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.54,0:30:16.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.96,0:30:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did he come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.67,0:30:26.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no, rain! Cover it up, cover it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.30,0:30:27.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.05,0:30:29.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why'd it have to rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.34,0:30:30.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talk about bad timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.31,0:30:34.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even with this sudden downpour,\Nthe crowd's still chanting Kid's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.31,0:30:39.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong, chopper #7? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.06,0:30:39.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.94,0:30:43.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The image from chopper #7 suddenly cut out.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.65,0:30:46.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is chopper #7. Everything looks right on my end.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.49,0:30:50.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think the rain's temporarily disrupting the image...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.70,0:30:56.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... Kid's accomplice is probably blocking the image somehow as part of Kid's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.87,0:30:59.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Kid has an assistant?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.33,0:31:05.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I've heard conflicting reports that it's either an old man or a young woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.59,0:31:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but we know he has somebody working for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.22,0:31:10.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-He's walking!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.42,0:31:11.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He started walking just like last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.59,0:31:17.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should I do, advisor? If we don't do something, he'll really steal it!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.35,0:31:20.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He won't get away with it that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.35,0:31:23.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stash the Blue Wonder inside the museum for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.55,0:31:24.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.63,0:31:26.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's his intelligence versus mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.72,0:31:30.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Scratches, preconceptions, the wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.07,0:31:32.97,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}An accomplice...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.10,0:31:37.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see! That's how it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.93,0:31:40.06,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I figured it out, Kaitō Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.06,0:31:43.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I know how you appeared, walked in the sky, and vanished!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.69,0:31:48.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And I know how you're planning to steal the Blue Wonder!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.20,0:31:50.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Advisor!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.32,0:31:53.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've finished moving the Blue Wonder indoors!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.66,0:31:56.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay! Then the next move's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.29,0:31:59.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Turn off all the lights in the museum!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.58,0:32:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.04,0:32:03.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.21,0:32:07.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a chance he may be\Nintercepting our camera feeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.55,0:32:12.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a minute. Isn't that\Nexactly what Kid would want?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.47,0:32:14.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got a better idea, Inspector Nakamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.35,0:32:23.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea how to stop a master\Nthief who can walk in mid-air like a wizard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.61,0:32:29.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what good will it do to store the jewel inside a darkened museum?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.61,0:32:32.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The point is to stop him from stealing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.95,0:32:38.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he can't get his hands on\Nthe Blue Wonder, then I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.62,0:32:40.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's a proposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.62,0:32:46.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I place you in command of this control centre,\Nwill you lend me a couple of your men?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.96,0:32:48.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My men?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.35,0:32:50.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.01,0:32:53.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a plan I've been working on all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.51,0:32:55.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.26,0:32:57.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.27,0:32:59.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.27,0:33:06.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that the helicopters got out of the way, I can see Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.02,0:33:08.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he's already so far away...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.61,0:33:10.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.24,0:33:15.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's Kaitō Kid! He's less than 100 metres from his target, the Blue Wonder!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.24,0:33:17.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! How are things going over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.45,0:33:20.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perfectly, Inspector Nakamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.29,0:33:23.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not even Kid will see through {\i1}this{\i} plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.63,0:33:29.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enough chit-chat! He might be tapping the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.26,0:33:31.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.17,0:33:32.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all going just as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.55,0:33:35.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll call back to tell you how it went.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.60,0:33:38.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.10,0:33:39.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.85,0:33:42.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something weird about Kid today!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.60,0:33:43.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.48,0:33:48.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You saw something that\Nlooked like a wire? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.11,0:33:51.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! There was a line or something shining near Kid's shoulder!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.82,0:33:53.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.57,0:33:58.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If what you're saying is true, then Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} isn't walking, he's hanging from that helicopter!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.99,0:34:01.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something's off, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.33,0:34:04.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His legs are moving, but he looks like he's dangling from a rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.83,0:34:08.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, chopper #7, the one that's flying over Kid! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.21,0:34:10.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, chopper #7!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.05,0:34:12.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chopper #7!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.18,0:34:18.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.30,0:34:22.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He disappeared just outside the museum!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.02,0:34:23.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it {\i1}was{\i} chopper #7!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.69,0:34:29.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His sidekick in chopper #7 used the smoke screen to pull him inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.36,0:34:33.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, your helicopters are all numbered, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.15,0:34:35.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. The number's written on the tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.20,0:34:37.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All helicopters circling the area!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.37,0:34:40.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Nakamori of the Police HQ!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.16,0:34:42.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid and his accomplice are in chopper #7!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.91,0:34:45.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Report in the position of chopper #7 right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.42,0:34:48.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep it surrounded until\Nthe police choppers arrive!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.21,0:34:51.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chopper #14 here!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.80,0:34:55.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a visual of chopper #7 above the front entrance to the museum!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.38,0:34:58.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good! Keep tailing it and don't lose sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.22,0:34:59.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.18,0:35:03.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chopper #35 here! Chopper #7's currently over Shiodome Park!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.93,0:35:08.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute... Shiodome Park is {\i1}behind{\i0} the museum!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.19,0:35:12.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chopper #28 here! Chopper #7's currently moving away from Shiodome...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.90,0:35:16.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-This is chopper #9! I see {\i1}two{\i} choppers\Nnumbered seven in front of Shiodome Park!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.65,0:35:19.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey... What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.32,0:35:23.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems most of our helicopters were painted with the number seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.79,0:35:26.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid must've changed the numbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.46,0:35:28.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid, how could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.92,0:35:31.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you see the number when you boarded the helicopter?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.00,0:35:34.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.01,0:35:37.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.30,0:35:40.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are some strange people at the museum entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.55,0:35:43.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's not just one or two people...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.31,0:35:47.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those are my men who I sent in there a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.31,0:35:52.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me the Blue Wonder's inside the case that the detective in the middle's carrying...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.27,0:35:53.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are they thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.94,0:35:57.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're carrying it out to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.66,0:36:00.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.16,0:36:01.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.45,0:36:03.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.37,0:36:06.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This case is empty. It's just a decoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.58,0:36:07.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A decoy?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.25,0:36:15.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jirokichi Suzuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} put the Blue Wonder in a trash bag and left through the back door disguised as a janitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.14,0:36:28.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's so funny...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.23,0:36:31.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...Kaitō Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.15,0:36:33.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.73,0:36:37.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm laughing because I managed to protect the jewel from Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.90,0:36:44.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moron. I knew who you were as soon as you showed up at the museum on this bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.37,0:36:48.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like now, you weren't\Nwearing your goggles.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.58,0:36:52.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's very hard for someone with contact lenses to ride a bike without wearing goggles.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.38,0:36:55.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even with a windscreen in front of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.84,0:36:59.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the pain of the wind hitting your eyes would cause you to tear up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.88,0:37:06.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The old man's a millionaire, but he rides around on this fancy bike without a single bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.39,0:37:10.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be hard for you to get a chance to drug him and take his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.89,0:37:17.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, I took the dog you left sleeping in this sidecar, Lupin, and left him in a shady spot in Shiodome Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.44,0:37:21.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You probably put him to sleep with a sleeping drug too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.53,0:37:25.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could I be Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.83,0:37:30.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was right next to you when Kid appeared this evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.87,0:37:35.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could you forget that wondrous moment when he walked in the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.29,0:37:38.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was no wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.05,0:37:42.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With an assistant, it's a simple trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.18,0:37:46.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Suzuki Financial Group relies on elite security guards rather than the police or the military!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.35,0:37:52.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it probably wasn't too hard for your accomplice to sneak in with a group of temporarily-hired pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.77,0:37:57.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last night, you suddenly appeared between two buildings,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.23,0:38:03.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and with a helicopter flying over you, it seemed impossible for you to be suspended from something.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.32,0:38:10.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, when the police and I ran up to the rooftops, we confirmed there were no wires between the buildings,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.54,0:38:13.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,making it look like you really were skywalking.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.91,0:38:18.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if that helicopter was flown by your assistant,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.63,0:38:20.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then the trick becomes simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.42,0:38:25.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First off, you flew over the buildings in your assistant's helicopter.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.14,0:38:29.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the helicopter, you hooked one end of a wire to the building's roof,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.72,0:38:35.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then flew to the opposite building and attached the other wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.81,0:38:37.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using the wire linking the two buildings,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.48,0:38:41.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and a pulley attached to your body, you moved to the middle of the wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.61,0:38:46.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You then threw off the black robe you were wearing as the smoke screen billowed around you,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.11,0:38:49.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and that's how Kaitō Kid made his entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.12,0:38:52.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next you had your sidekick fly the helicopter over you,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.83,0:38:56.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and have them wind up a thin wire made from fishing line until it was taut,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.29,0:39:00.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,which you'd connected to yourself before leaving the helicopter.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.13,0:39:07.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, you removed the pulley and had the helicopter quickly retrieve the wire connecting the buildings.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.30,0:39:12.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that point, it looked like you were hanging from nothing, so your levitation trick was complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.81,0:39:17.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you just had to pretend to walk as the helicopter moved forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.44,0:39:22.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You had a tape recorder in your pocket playing the sound of footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.53,0:39:24.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the wire swayed a little, you walked a small step,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.44,0:39:26.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and if it swayed a lot,\Nyou walked a larger step.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.45,0:39:32.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was an amazing performance to make people think you weren't hanging from anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.24,0:39:36.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then after walking for a bit, you cast off your white suit together with the smoke screen,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.29,0:39:37.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,had the searchlight move off you,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.75,0:39:42.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and had your assistant pull you up into the helicopter to make it look like you vanished in mid-air.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.75,0:39:48.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the Kid who appeared tonight was just a dummy with moving legs set up to distract the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.43,0:39:51.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You made it appear the same way, with the smoke screen and the helicopter.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.19,0:39:54.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it was just hanging there, so it was obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.52,0:39:58.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But boy, didn't you climb up to the rooftop to watch Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.52,0:40:03.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If there was something hanging off a helicopter, you would've seen it, no matter how thin the wire was!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.44,0:40:06.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I blame the wind and my own preconceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.40,0:40:09.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was stupid of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.07,0:40:14.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was completely convinced you weren't suspended\Nby a wire, because I'd seen a helicopter fly over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.79,0:40:19.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, I'd been looking for a wire connected to the rooftop, and didn't find one.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.62,0:40:24.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you left traces of that wire on the rooftops of those two buildings.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.21,0:40:29.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Scratches left by the hooks on the end of the wires when they were pulled up by the helicopter.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.18,0:40:34.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But still, you checked the footage of Kid from last night over and over, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.18,0:40:42.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It depends on the video's resolution, but either way it's very hard to see such a thin wire on a monitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.44,0:40:46.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A downward shot of Kid might've revealed it, as the wires would pass in front of him,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.53,0:40:49.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but the only helicopter that could shoot that was chopper #7, piloted by your sidekick.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.53,0:40:56.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That chopper sent footage from the previously aired Suzuki Museum TV Special overlaid with your own footage.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.45,0:41:02.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were sending edited footage from chopper #7, so there weren't any wires that could show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.46,0:41:07.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why your accomplice stopped transmitting when the rain started, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.96,0:41:11.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The aerial shots in the TV special didn't include people with umbrellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.84,0:41:15.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your flashy demonstration last night
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.31,0:41:18.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was to make it look like you'd come from the sky, so checks on the ground would be reduced,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.68,0:41:23.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so that you could disguise yourself as Jirokichi\NSuzuki and pass through without being checked.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.48,0:41:30.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you got forgetful. I clearly saw you on TV riding the bike without goggles.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.32,0:41:35.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I didn't forget the goggles. I just couldn't wear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.70,0:41:38.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'd mess up my disguise!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.54,0:41:40.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.21,0:41:45.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That accomplice of yours in chopper #7 is probably surrounded by the police by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.04,0:41:49.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah, it's fine. The police are probably in a huge panic
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.67,0:41:53.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,due to all the choppers having the number 7 on their tails.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.47,0:41:55.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the choppers?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.51,0:41:58.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. You put a sticker with the number 7 on all the choppers,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.97,0:42:02.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,followed by another, lightly pasted sticker with the correct number.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.77,0:42:06.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The second sticker would fly off in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.36,0:42:11.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. All the pilots got on their helicopters without realising
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.65,0:42:15.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that they'd end up being chased under suspicion of being my accomplice.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.62,0:42:18.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the chaos, my sidekick will escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.87,0:42:23.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Into the blue wonder, the miracle of the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.58,0:42:28.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sky? The Blue Wonder's 'blue' represents the blue of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.17,0:42:32.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Same thing. The sea's blue because it reflects the blue sky, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.51,0:42:35.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the same with detectives and phantom thieves.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.47,0:42:37.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We may seem like opposites,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.76,0:42:41.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but in the end we're both\Ndedicated to opening the door
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.02,0:42:45.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,leading to the secrets people keep, using curiosity as a key.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.02,0:42:49.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot. The sea and sky are blue because of refraction and diffusion of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.73,0:42:53.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're blue for completely different reasons. Don't mix them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.95,0:42:57.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As proof of that, puddles aren't blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.32,0:42:59.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You never dream, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.62,0:43:03.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't see the truth if you get hung up on dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.08,0:43:07.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, do you really think you can capture me with that tranquiliser dart?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.50,0:43:10.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I fall asleep at this speed, we'll have a huge crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.59,0:43:13.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I won't shoot until the bike stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.84,0:43:17.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I already called Inspector\NNakamori to come and pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.84,0:43:20.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmph. I'm not going to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.01,0:43:22.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you forget what old Jirokichi told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.77,0:43:28.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This bike's been modified to speed it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.77,0:43:32.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So long, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.65,0:43:34.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You can keep the jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.44,0:43:37.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It isn't what I'm looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.95,0:43:41.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I only came because the old prune picked a fight with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.28,0:44:12.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.52,0:44:38.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You never dream, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.82,0:44:41.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't be stupid. Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.61,0:44:47.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I have a dream, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.61,0:46:14.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did anything show?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.65,0:46:18.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, how was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.53,0:46:21.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you enjoy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.57,0:46:28.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though the reason why Uncle took Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} as an enemy was kinda dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.04,0:46:34.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the end, the four-eyed brat saved the Blue Wonder. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.08,0:46:37.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you wannabe detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.55,0:46:48.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next time, I'll escape from both you {\i1}and{\i0} the cops with even more awesome magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.99,0:46:50.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.07,0:47:04.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That goes for you too...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.78,0:47:07.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure to catch you next time,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.11,0:47:08.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so {\i1}you{\i0} prepare yourself.
